This software is built with Maven; get it from http://maven.apache.org/.

To build:
mvn {compile|test|package}

You can use Eclipse either by running:
mvn eclipse:eclipse

or installing the m2eclipse plugin (which I've found a little flaky).


To hack on the Android app in Eclipse, read:
http://www.sonatype.com/books/mvnref-book/reference/android-dev-sect-config-build.html


#!/jon

